snippet.textDisplay: what's the fucking point of having one of the finest drummers in the subcontinent if you're going to have the most bland, copy pasted loops for the percussion? i see great players like mithun pretending to play random things that aren't heard. and gaboo!!! the king of drums!!! why the fuck is he singing????? when he was shooting this video he performed at jatra and the music heard there was genuine, not this prepackaged loop factory bullshit. (don't get me wrong, it's almost always bullshit, but usually it's just a slap in the face of good taste, leaving other pedantries unharmed.)
